posting_body: ['Amber Creek', '13438 Oneida Lane, Thornton, CO, 80602', 'Use this link for more info:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 3', 'OR Text', '3', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team.', 'Welcome Home to Amber Creek', 'This is a 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath, approximately 1468 Sq.', 'Ft.', "From the moment you arrive at Amber Creek, you'll feel like you've come home.", 'Our beautiful community is conveniently located in Thornton Colorado, just 10 miles north of Denver and within proximity to the Denver-Aurora-Lakewood metropolitan area.', 'Enjoy small-town charm near big city amenities!', 'These brand-new, rental homes have carefully curated floor plans for any lifestyle.', 'We offer both three and four-bedroom floor plans to choose from with two-car garages, fenced-in backyards, and more.', 'Experience maintenance-free living so you worry less and enjoy more!', 'Surrounded by scenic views with enviable community amenities and a team dedicated to providing quick and excellent service, Amber Creek has it all.', 'Features', '- Fenced-in Backyards', '- Rental Homes', '- Three and Four Bedrooms', '- Two-car Garages', '- Brand New', 'Community Amenities', '- Surrounded by Scenic Views', '- Within Proximity to the Denver-Aurora-Lakewood Metropolitan Area', '- On-Site Maintenance', '- Dedicated Team', '- 10 Miles North of Denver', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Saturday: 10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Sunday: 12:00PM-6:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Dogs allowed', 'Cats allowed', 'YB09AEZkEb']
